dct_title_s: Tabula Terræ Canaan Abrahæ tempore et ante adventum filior Israel cum vicinis et finitimis regionib
dct_alternative_sm: Tabvla Terræ Canaan Abrahæ tempore et ante adventvm filior Israel cvm vicinis et finitimis regionib
dct_description_sm: Shows topography, vegetation, waterways, routes, ports.
Pictorial vignettes of settlements, ships, sea monsters.
Appears in Arias Montanus' Biblia polyglotta, Antwerp: Christophe Plantin, 1572.
